overview.en: AfroDex Token (AfroX) is the primary native token of Africa's biggest decentralized exchange; AfroDex Labs. AfroX is Proof of Stake erc20 & can be staked to participate in minting or used for listing and more.
overview.zh: AfroDex令牌（AfroX）是非洲最大的去中心化交易所的主要本地令牌； AfroDex實驗室。 AfroX是權益證明erc20，可以放心參與鑄造或用於上市等等。
